<div n="r" type="textpart">
<div n="A" subtype="fragment" type="textpart"><ab>
<lb n="1"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> ἀναγκάζηται ἀθανάτους τὰς ψ<supplied reason="lost">υ</supplied>χ<supplied reason="lost">ὰς ὁμολογεῖν, ἀ</supplied>
<lb n="2" break="no"/><supplied reason="lost">ξιώσο</supplied><unclear>μέν</unclear> π<supplied reason="lost">ο</supplied><unclear>υ</unclear>, εἰ ἀληθῆ λέγε<unclear>ι</unclear> ὁ ταῦτα λέγων, <supplied reason="lost">τ</supplied><unclear>ὴ</unclear><supplied reason="lost">ν ἀδικίαν θανά</supplied>
<lb n="3" break="no"/><supplied reason="lost">σιμον</supplied> εἶναι τῶ<supplied reason="lost">ι</supplied> ἔχοντι ὥσπερ νόσον,<g type="middot"/> καὶ ὑπ᾽αὐ<unclear>τ</unclear><supplied reason="lost">οῦ, τοῦ ἀποκτει</supplied>
<lb n="4" break="no"/><supplied reason="lost">νύντο</supplied><unclear>ς</unclear> τῆ<unclear>ι</unclear> ἑ<unclear>αυ</unclear>τοῦ φύσει, ἀποθνῄσκειν τοὺς <supplied reason="lost">λαμβάνον</supplied>
<lb n="5" break="no"/><supplied reason="lost">τας αὐ</supplied>τό, τοὺς μὲν μάλιστα <unclear>θ</unclear>ᾶττον,<g type="middot"/> τοὺς δ<g type="apostrophe"/> ἧττ<unclear>ο</unclear><supplied reason="lost">ν σχολαί</supplied>
<lb n="6" break="no"/><supplied reason="lost">τερον,</supplied> ἀλλὰ μὴ<surplus>ν</surplus> ὥσπερ νῦν δ<unclear>ιὰ</unclear> τοῦτο <hi rend="diaeresis">ὑ</hi>π᾽ ἄλλων δί<supplied reason="lost">κην ἐπιτι</supplied>
<lb n="7" break="no"/><supplied reason="lost">θέντ</supplied>ων <app type="editorial"><lem>ἀποθνῄσκουσιν</lem><rdg resp="m2">ἀποθνῄσκ<add place="below">ω</add>σιν</rdg></app> οἱ ἄδικοι.<g type="dipunct"/> μὰ Δία, ἦ δ<g type="apostrophe"/> <hi rend="asper">ὅ</hi>ς,<g type="dipunct"/> <supplied reason="lost">οὐκ ἄρα πάν</supplied>
<lb n="8" break="no"/><supplied reason="lost">δεινο</supplied><unclear>ν</unclear> φανε<supplied reason="lost">ῖτ</supplied><unclear>αι</unclear> ἡ ἀδικία,<g type="middot"/> εἰ θανάσιμον ἔσται τ<supplied reason="lost">ῷ λαμβά</supplied>
<lb n="9" break="no"/><supplied reason="lost">νοντι – ἀ</supplied>παλ<supplied reason="lost">λαγὴ γ</supplied>ὰρ ἂν εἴη κα<unclear>κ</unclear>ῶν¬ –<g type="middot"/> ἀλλὰ μᾶλλον <unclear>ο</unclear>ἶ<unclear>μ</unclear><supplied reason="lost">αι αὐτὴν</supplied>
