<lb n="11" break="no"/><supplied reason="lost">περ οἷόν τε, τὸν δ᾽</supplied> ἔχο<supplied reason="lost">ντα</supplied> <unclear>κ</unclear>αὶ μᾶλλον <supplied reason="lost">ζωτικὸν</supplied> <unclear>π</unclear><supplied reason="lost">αρ</supplied><unclear>έ</unclear><supplied reason="lost">χ</supplied><unclear>ουσ</unclear><supplied reason="lost">αν,</supplied>
